#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an6.108"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an6.108:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 6 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 6 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.108:0.2"
msgid "11. Tikavagga "
msgstr "11. Triads "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an6.108:0.3"
msgid "108. Duccaritasutta "
msgstr "108. Bad Conduct "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an6.108:1.1"
msgid "“Tayome, bhikkhave, dhammā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these three things. "

msgctxt "an6.108:1.2"
msgid "Katame tayo? "
msgstr "What three? "

msgctxt "an6.108:1.3"
msgid "Kāyaduccaritaṃ, vacīduccaritaṃ, manoduccaritaṃ. "
msgstr "Bad conduct by way of body, speech, and mind. "

msgctxt "an6.108:1.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, tayo dhammā. "
msgstr "These are the three things. "

msgctxt "an6.108:1.5"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, tiṇṇaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya tayo dhammā bhāvetabbā. "
msgstr "To give up these three things you should develop three things. "

msgctxt "an6.108:1.6"
msgid "Katame tayo? "
msgstr "What three? "

msgctxt "an6.108:1.7"
msgid "Kāyaduccaritassa pahānāya kāyasucaritaṃ bhāvetabbaṃ, vacīduccaritassa pahānāya vacīsucaritaṃ bhāvetabbaṃ, manoduccaritassa pahānāya manosucaritaṃ bhāvetabbaṃ. "
msgstr "You should develop good bodily conduct to give up bad bodily conduct, good verbal conduct to give up bad verbal conduct, and good mental conduct to give up bad mental conduct. "

msgctxt "an6.108:1.8"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, tiṇṇaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya ime tayo dhammā bhāvetabbā”ti. "
msgstr "These are the three things you should develop to give up those three things.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.108:1.9"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
